#. type: Plain text
#: build/C/man5/acct.5:94
msgid ""
"The I<comp_t> data type is a floating-point value consisting of a 3-bit, "
"base-8 exponent, and a 13-bit mantissa.  A value, I<c>, of this type can be "
"converted to a (long) integer as follows:"
