"admin-guide/cgroup-v1/hugetlb.rst> (or I<Documentation/cgroup-v1/hugetlb."
"txt> in Linux 5.2 and earlier)."
msgstr ""

#. type: TP
#: build/C/man7/cgroups.7:407
#, no-wrap
msgid "I<pids> (since Linux 4.3; B<CONFIG_CGROUP_PIDS>)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
