#: build/C/man7/cgroups.7:616
msgid ""
"For more changes, see the I<Documentation/admin-guide/cgroup-v2.rst> file in "
"the kernel source (or I<Documentation/cgroup-v2.txt> in Linux 4.17 and "
"earlier)."
msgstr ""

